## 8. ⚠️ SAFE / INTERACTIVE MODE — Decision Gate

Since the trust mode is `{{ mode }}`, this routing decision **requires user
confirmation** before the pipeline proceeds.  The routing engine will set
`pending_confirmation` in state.json and pause.

**If you are reading this via an Aider session:**
Do NOT proceed to the next phase.  Wait for the routing decision to be
confirmed by the user or the loop-aider state machine.

